postReview.title: Aston Villa 3-2 Everton: Duran screamer completes comeback for hosts
postReview.description: Jhon Duran's blistering 76th minute strike and an Ollie Watkins brace completed a Aston Villa's comeback as Everton lose 3-2 twice in a row.

preReview.title: Emery hoping competitiveness translates into first home win
preReview.description: Aston Villa lost their first home game this season, but Unai Emery is determined to avoid the same result against a struggling Everton side.
